GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from 18th May, 2023:
Shri Kiren Rijiju relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Law and Justice.
He assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of Earth Sciences.
Shri Arjun Ram Meghwal assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of State
(Independent Charge) of the Ministry of Law and Justice. He will continue to hold the
charge of the office of the Minister of State in the Ministry of Parliamentary Affairs; and
the charge of the office of the Minister of State in the Ministry of Culture.
Prof. S. P. Singh Baghel relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in
the Ministry of Law and Justice. He assumed the charge of the office of the Minister of
State in the Ministry of Health and Family Welfare.
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
New Delhi, the 18th May, 2023
Copy forwarded for information to:
Secretary to the President.
Secretary to the Vice-President.
Copy forwarded for information to the Vice-Chairperson, NITI Aayog.
Copy also forwarded for information to:
Principal Secretary to the Prime Minister.
